    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"ant.png\" width=\"887\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/ant.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433131447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=887&amp;height=613\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644703/ant.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433131447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"613\" data-width=\"887\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644715\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"ant.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644703\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b481ba2c-7eff-461e-a154-b4d4300d18bb\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/ant.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433131447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=887&amp;height=613 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/ant.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433131447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=887&amp;height=613 1x\"></span><p> </p><p>We can create a material using the RenderMan Shelf or in the shop pane.</p><h3 id=\"CreatingAMaterial-UsingtheMATPane\"> Using the MAT Pane</h3><ul><li><p>Create a Material, PxrMaterialBuilder. <em>Note that this node will filter out unsupported nodes</em></p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"450\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/rfh_createMaterialBuilder.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132017&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=450&amp;height=344\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644703/rfh_createMaterialBuilder.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132017&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644748\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_createMaterialBuilder.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644703\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e5462616-b5d3-4fca-b659-5e03336d71a3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/rfh_createMaterialBuilder.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132017&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=648&amp;height=496 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/rfh_createMaterialBuilder.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132017&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=450&amp;height=344 1x\"></span> </p><ul><li><p>Dive into the Material Builder (double click) and create a BxDF VOP, PxrSurface to connect to the output_collect (we recommend using a PxrLayerSurface if you know you will be layering effects)<br/><br/></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"442\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/rfh_createPxrSurface.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=442&amp;height=338\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644703/rfh_createPxrSurface.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"496\" data-width=\"648\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644751\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_createPxrSurface.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644703\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ca574a9b-de9c-4292-9e29-294d5cbe3b66\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/rfh_createPxrSurface.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=648&amp;height=496 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/rfh_createPxrSurface.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=442&amp;height=338 1x\"></span><p><br/></p><ul><li><p>Wire the bxdf into the output_collect</p></li></ul><p><br/></p><ul><li><p>Add <strong>Pattern</strong> VOP to modify the Bxdf setting. Below we wire a PxrTexture into the Diffuse Color. We also add a PxrDisplace with a texture to the second shader slot on the out_collect. (If displacing, be sure your object has a set non-zero displacement bound)<br/><br/><br/></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"482\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/rfh_exampleMatNetwork.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=482&amp;height=368\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644703/rfh_exampleMatNetwork.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"496\" data-width=\"648\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644754\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_exampleMatNetwork.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644703\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"223fdd70-f973-4b55-b570-4afa8e1d1c58\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/rfh_exampleMatNetwork.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=648&amp;height=496 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/rfh_exampleMatNetwork.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=482&amp;height=368 1x\"></span><p><br/></p><h3 id=\"CreatingAMaterial-AssignMaterial\">Assign Material</h3><p>To assign the material to your object, simply drag the material op path to Material.</p><p><br/></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"482\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/rfh_assignMaterialPath.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=482&amp;height=368\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644703/rfh_assignMaterialPath.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"496\" data-width=\"648\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644757\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_assignMaterialPath.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644703\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6b541bff-ae13-4e14-b811-029573e38de6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/rfh_assignMaterialPath.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=648&amp;height=496 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644703/rfh_assignMaterialPath.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433132182&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=482&amp;height=368 1x\"></span>"
    }
